   Sort Method: quicksort  Memory: 42kB
   ->  Seq Scan on printer  (cost=0.00..37.77 rows=222 width=51) (actual time=0.218..26.032 rows=222 loops=1)
 Total runtime: 26.733 ms
(5 rows)

